Successfully implemented a comprehensive enhancement suite that transforms the interface from single-generation focused to a powerful tool for systematic audio generation, comparison, and parameter exploration. Additionally fixed a critical startup issue that prevented the GUI from launching without pre-specified models. All changes maintain backward compatibility while adding significant new functionality.

